message.body: I WANT TO SEE YOU THIS BREAK
YEAHHHH UUUUU!!!!!!!!!
EVEN IF THAT WAS A MASS TEXT, I'LL TAKE IT!!!
IT WASNTTTTTT
What do you have in mind???
Hmmm idk I haven't thought about specifics yet. What do you think?
I'm terrible with coming up with plans... We could go to a park....go eat....wander.....
We will figure it out but we need a date first!
I kind of want to see Beth.....but idk how to get back into tech
LMFAO BETH. Yeah I kinda want to visit tech too. I can get you in through mr Stevens
I don't know how badly I want to go back but if we do it'll have to be this week....otherwise it's vacation
Yeah I'm not going till January. When do you go back to school?
January sixth is my flight....ugh....
SO SOOOON :'(
I know :-( THREE WEEKS IS NOTHING
Well are you enjoying school at least
Slowly but surely!! People embrace how weird I am!!! Well, a few of them. Others still choose to see me as that small Asian girl but they don't know tha I ain't about that life
Lmaoooo oh daisy you are fitting in! That's good. Let da h8rz h8.
How do you like Emory???
It's awesoooome. I really like it. I feel comfortable there and acclimated and everyone is really nice. I feel like I'm being inspired to be a better person every day in that environment
Will, I believe you have found the *real* college experience. I'm so glad you chose Emory!!
Omg me too! I like to think of it that Emory chose me~
You are in love LOL I just feel it
It really is a great place. Still jelly of u in Chicago though
I feel guilty for not enjoying it more...
The city or the school?
Both. I've been so buried in my classes....

Yeah that's understandable. Well you don't have to feel pressured to like it, you have a lot more time there to find your niche. I've also been too busy to go out into Atlanta as much as I'd like, and it's hard to get involved in too many things on campus too
I just don't want to be too focused on grades... I want to but I don't. I've never had so much on my hands before and it's nice. I just want to handle it better

Yeah I understand what you mean. It's like a weird time when you have access to a lot but can't fit it all in your schedule. But getting out there and meeting people kinda reminds you why you're there in the first place
Yeah but it's hard for me to do that part... I just want to find things I like and do those
Yeah it's easier said than done but you can do it I believe in you!!!! People love you and there are so many options for you!!!!
:') you are so supportive!!! Thank you!! You just keep on keeping on!!!
:D You have to or else you will go crazy and get discouraged :'( </3
